
 FOR DEPOLYING APP ON HEROKU :
 -----------------------------

   git push heroku for_heroku:master
   
   heroku  rake sunspot:solr:start
    
   heroku rake sunspot:reindex 
    
   heroku rake db:migrate db:seed
    
   gem install heroku --no-ri --no-rdoc
	
   heroku create (will ask heroku account login and create app overthere.)

   git push heroku master

   git push heroku for_heroku:master (if your code is on any other branch other than master)


heroku config : 
  160  
  161: $ heroku config:set GITHUB_USERNAME=joesmith
  162  Adding config vars and restarting myapp... done, v12
  163  GITHUB_USERNAME: joesmith
  164  
  165: $ heroku config
  166  GITHUB_USERNAME: joesmith
  167  OTHER_VAR:    production
  168  
  169: $ heroku config:get GITHUB_USERNAME
  170  joesmith
  171  
  172: $ heroku config:unset GITHUB_USERNAME
  173  Unsetting GITHUB_USERNAME and restarting myapp... done, v13
  174  
  175: heroku config:set WEBSOLR_URL=
  176  
  177  WEBSOLR_URL    =>




